doc.name: SIC_To_NAICS_2012
doc.description:
The reference table contains Standard Industrial Classification (SIC) codes and descriptions and maps to the 2012 North American Industry Classification System (NAICS) codes and descriptions.
Note that there is not a direct relationship between the SIC and NAICS codes, some SIC codes have been expanded out to multiple NAICS codes
